gs-3845780">曼彻斯特邮政的新世纪大厅举办Heaton Park演出的官方Oasis Afterparties，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/A-Manchester-mural-depicting-Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-of-Oasis.-Credit-Christopher-Furlong_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="曼彻斯特壁画，描绘了绿洲的利亚姆和诺埃尔·加拉格尔。信用 - 克里斯托弗·弗隆/盖蒂图像" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/A-Manchester-mural-depicting-Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-of-Oasis.-Credit-Christopher-Furlong_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/A-Manchester-mural-depicting-Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-of-Oasis.-Credit-Christopher-Furlong_Getty-Images-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/A-Manchester-mural-depicting-Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-of-Oasis.-Credit-Christopher-Furlong_Getty-Images-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/A-Manchester-mural-depicting-Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-of-Oasis.-Credit-Christopher-Furlong_Getty-Images-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/A-Manchester-mural-depicting-Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-of-Oasis.-Credit-Christopher-Furlong_Getty-Images-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/A-Manchester-mural-depicting-Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-of-Oasis.-Credit-Christopher-Furlong_Getty-Images-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>曼彻斯特的新世纪大厅将举办官方的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>亮点，这是在今年7月的一些Heaton Park演出之后举行的。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-manchester-sifters-mural-3790147">“城市中有明显的嗡嗡声”：曼彻斯特的景色在绿洲回来时</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>绿洲的“ Live &#39;25</em>聚会之旅”将于7月4日星期五在加的夫开始，将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">英国长期的约会视为他们今年在欧洲唯一的演出</a>，然后乐队前往<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-reunion-tour-dates-in-north-america-and-mexico-buy-tickets-3798246">北美</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-south-american-reunion-tour-dates-the-brothers-are-coming-buy-tickets-3809661">南美</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-australian-dates-of-live-25-reunion-tour-buy-tickets-3800091">澳大利亚</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-south-korean-and-japan-dates-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3814881">亚洲的</a>体育场。</p><p>这包括7月11日，12日，16日，19日和20日在曼彻斯特的希顿公园举行的五场演出。</p><p>各方将以Bez（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">周一快乐</a>），Clint Boon（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/inspiral-carpets">Inspiral Carpets</a> ），Mani（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stone-roses">石玫瑰</a>），Tin Tin Tin（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/new-order">New Order</a> Tour DJ），Col White（Vinyl Revival）和Ricco（Creamfields）（Creamfields）为特色。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHHAom7tWH7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 a