ads/2025/03/Calvin-Harris-2025-Ushuaia-Ibiza-double-residency-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Calvin Harris 2025UshuaïaIbiza双重居住海报。信用：出版" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Calvin-Harris-2025-Ushuaia-Ibiza-double-residency-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Calvin-Harris-2025-Ushuaia-Ibiza-double-residency-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Calvin-Harris-2025-Ushuaia-Ibiza-double-residency-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Calvin-Harris-2025-Ushuaia-Ibiza-double-residency-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Calvin-Harris-2025-Ushuaia-Ibiza-double-residency-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Calvin-Harris-2025-Ushuaia-Ibiza-double-residency-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Calvin-Harris">加尔文·哈里斯（Calvin Harris）</a>将在<a href="https://www.theushuaiaexperience.com/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UshuaïaIbiza</a>拥有双重居留权，这是历史上第一次这样做。</p><p>赢得格莱美奖的制片人，DJ和词曲作者将在今年夏天在UshuaïaIbiza周二和周五在UshuaïaIbiza接管25个精心策划的演出。从5月30日至9月12日，哈里斯将在每个星期五和7月1日至8月26日进行演出，他将在每个星期二演出。</p><p>哈里斯（Harris）的UshuaïaIbiza居住地的单夜门票起价为120欧元（100英镑）。您可以访问<a href="https://www.theushuaiaexperience.com/en/club/calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票并找到有关活动的更多信息。</p><p>新闻稿承诺“ 25种精心策划的节目，与以前所见，提供了世界排斥的居留权。”在谈到即将到来的居留权时，哈里斯分享道：“这是以前从未做过的事情，我正在嗡嗡作响，成为第一位在UshuaïaIbiza拥有双重居留权的艺术家。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DHELX5koli5/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 