/album/kae-tempest-the-line-is-a-curve-review-3199667">四星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>将“ The Line Is Curve”描述为“经常令人眼花azz乱”。它写道：“放手的过程产生了一份记录，备受赞誉的声音可以比以往任何时候都更加广度和深度探索人类的情感。”</p><p>单打“更大的压力”（以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brockhampton">布罗克汉普顿</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kevin-abstract">凯文摘要</a>为特色）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/kae-tempest-shares-salt-coast-from-upcoming-album-the-line-is-a-curve-3154855">“盐海岸”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/kae-tempest-lianne-la-havas-collaboration-single-no-prizes-listen-video-3177524">“无奖品”</a> （以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lianne-la-havas">lianne la havas</a>为特色）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/kae-tempest-shares-emotive-new-song-featuring-fontaines-d-c-s-grian-chatten-3194577">“ Move”</a> （以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-dc">Fontaines DC</a>的Grian Chatten为特色），这使它被抢占。</p><div id="playlist-player-jwplayer"><div class="playlist-player-container"></div></div><p> Kae Tempest在本月举行的三场亲密<a href="https://www.nme.com">英国</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kae-tempest-to-play-three-intimate-uk-shows-this-month-cant-wait-to-get-back-at-it-3845744">节目中演出：“等不及要回来”</a> 。</p> ;
